<div><head>鄱陽記</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-1a.2">《清灣》</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-1a.3">清灣在縣東南七里，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-1a.4">隋開皇中太守梁文謙涖宮清潔，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-1a.5">取此灣水以自供，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-1a.6">後人思其德，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-1a.7">號為清灣。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-1a.8">《沙堆》</seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-2a.2">新昌水有一沙堆在縣東北五十里，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-2a.3">其形狀如覆船，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-2a.4">鮮凈特異，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-2a.5">每年豐稔，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-2a.6">其沙即堆積如舊；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-2a.7">若砂移向岸，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-2a.8">其年儉，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-2a.9">古來相傳，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-2a.10">以為常驗。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-3a.2">《白雲城》</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-3a.3">白雲在縣西南，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-3a.4">旁對干亭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-3a.5">而峙焉跨古城之危，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-3a.6">瞰長江之深。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-3a.7">隋州剌史劉長卿題詩曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-3a.8">孤城上與白雲齊。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-3a.9">因以白雲為名。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-4a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-4a" ed="CHANT" n="001-4a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-4a.2">《三鐵鑊》</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-4a.3">弋陽嶺上多密岩，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-4a.4">宋元嘉中，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-4a.5">有人見其岩內三鐵鑊，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-4a.6">鑊各容百斛，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-4a.7">中生蓮花，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-4a.8">他人往尋，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-4a.9">不知所在。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-5a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-5a" ed="CHANT" n="001-5a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-5a.2">《望夫岡》</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-5a.3">鄱陽西有望夫岡。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-5a.4">昔縣人陳明與梅氏為姻未成，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-5a.5">而妖魅許迎婦去，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-5a.6">明請卜者決云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-5a.7">西北行五十里求之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-5a.8">明如言，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-5a.9">見大穴深邃無底，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-5a.10">以繩懸入，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-5a.11">遂得其婦，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-5a.12">乃令婦先出，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-5a.13">而明所將鄰人秦文遂不取明，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-5a.14">其妻乃自誓執志登此岡首而望其夫，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1730_CHANT_001-5a.15">因以名焉。<lb/></seg>
</p>
